{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji24.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致刘少奇电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致刘少奇电！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年3月20日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此次工委和华北、华东、华中各负责同志一起，彻底检讨各项领导工作上的错误缺点，并由此获得纠正，走上正轨，极为欣慰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们明日动身东移，由此到兴县走路及谈话十天，坐车去代县五天，走路到你处十天，约卯删可到你处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东致刘少奇电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1948,"month":3,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":176,"page_end":176},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}